      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for rsync fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2025-10158: Out of bounds array access via negative index (bsc#1254441).\n- CVE-2026-41035: count of entries mismatch can lead to a use-after-free (bsc#1262223).\n",
